title: DB2: Instance Logfile Usage
agents: aix, linux
catalog: app/db2
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors amount of free logfile space.
 You can configure limits for absolute and percentage free space.

 This check needs the mk_db2 plugin installed in the agent.

item:
 The DB2 instance name followed by a : and the database name, e.g. db2ilog1:REST1

inventory:
 One service is created for each database.

